flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Monthly S&OP cycle initiation]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve IBP plan variants]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: AutoML - Perform financial impact assessment]
  N2 --> N3[PB: Rules - Identify discrepancies between plans]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze profitability by product/region]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Remote Functions - Integrate CapEx requirements]
  N5 --> N6[Cortex: AutoML - Evaluate financial scenarios]
  N6 --> N7[UI: UI Screens - Present recommendations]
  N7 --> N8{Decision: Assess financial impact of the integrated IBP plan on revenue and alignment with ops; identify discrepancies between operational plans and financial targets; analyze profitability by vehicle line and region; integrate CapEx requirements into the overall financial plan; evaluate multiple financial and operational scenarios}
  N7 --> Z1[Outcome: Optimized revenue, EBITDA, and working capital through integrated financial and operational planning]
  N8 -->|Discrepancies identified| B1[Recommend corrective actions]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Aligned plans]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|Low profitability detected| B2[Recommend divestment]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Optimized EBITDA]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N8 -->|High CapEx impact| B3[Defer or scale projects]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Balanced CapEx]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]